StructureDefinition-aq

source file: source/pages/_includes/aq-intro.md

The Argonaut Adaptvie Q profile sets the minimum expectations for the Questionnaire resource for the adaptive questionnaire use case. It defines the contained structure that is passed between the Client and Server using the $next-q operation and records the questionnaire questions and calculated scores from the adaptive questionnaire.
